Name: lung non-squamous non-small cell carcinoma
Definition: A lung non-small cell carcinoma that is characterized by the lack of evidence of squamous differentiation.

Name: lung squamous cell carcinoma
Definition: A non-small cell lung carcinoma that has_material_basis_in the squamous cell.

Name: lung large cell carcinoma
Definition: An ovarian carcinoma that is characterized by large pleiomorphic cells with large round or oval nuclei
